National Assembly: Debate as Urgent Matter of National Public Importance (Mr K J Mileham): Fuel price hikes (95), Hybrid Meeting Platform, 15th June 2022, CAPE TOWN - Parliament is holding a debate on South Africa’s record petrol price increases.
This follows a request by the Democratic Alliance.
MPs will focus on the country’s record petrol price hikes, and possible interventions to structurally change how the basic fuel price is calculated.